                            <comment id="13143240" author="gagravarr" created="Thu, 3 Nov 2011 15:34:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;How close is it to picking the correct one? (i.e. what are the various scores for all the charset detectors?)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13433290" author="kkrugler" created="Mon, 13 Aug 2012 16:57:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I added a test case for this, and in trunk it seems to be fixed. You get back ISO-8859-1 if you don&apos;t set any incoming charset, and you get UTF-8 if you specify UTF-8 in the incoming metadata.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
